The paper deals with the problem of phase retrieval, which is a topic in information theory (cs.IT) and signal processing (cs.SP). The proposed algorithm is specifically designed for sparse signals, which is a common problem in computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also mentions the potential suitability of the algorithm for large scale problems such as images, which could fall under numerical analysis (cs.NA).
